ham"}
{"title_page": "List of Diptera families", "text_new": "This is a list of the families of the order [[Fly|Diptera]] (true flies). The classification is based largely on Pape ''et al.'' (2011). Many of the fossil species are of uncertain placement and are retained in separate lists broadly under Nematocera and Brachycera.<ref>{{cite book| author1=Pape, Thomas| author2= Blagoderov, Vladimir| author3= Mostovski, Michail B.| year=2011| chapter= Order Diptera Linnaeus, 1758|editor=Zhang, Z. Q.| title=Animal biodiversity: an outline of higher-level classification and survey of taxonomic richness |pages= 222\u2013229| publisher=Magnolia Press|url = https://static-curis.ku.dk/portal/files/182118915/Pape_2011_Order_Diptera_Linnaeus.pdf}}</ref>\n{{cladogram|align = right|title=Graphical overview\n|cladogram={{clade\n |label1=Diptera\n |1={{clade\n  |label1=Nematocera\n  |1={{clade\n   |1=Deuterophlebiomorpha\n   |2=Nymphomyiomorpha\n   |3=Tipulomorpha\n   |4=Ptychopteromorpha\n   |5=Psychodomorpha\n   |6=Culicomorpha\n   |label7=Neodiptera\n   |7={{clade\n    |1=Perissommatomorpha\n    |2=Bibionomorpha\n   }}\n  }}\n  |label2=Brachycera\n  |2={{clade\n   |1=Orthorrhapha\n   |label2=Eremoneura\n   |2={{clade\n    |label1=Cyclorrhapha\n    |1={{clade\n     |1=Aschiza\n     |label2=Schizophora\n     |2={{clade\n      |1=Acalyptratae\n      |2=Calyptratae\n     }}\n    }}\n   }}\n  }}\n }}\n}}\n}}\n==Nematocera==\n=== Infraorder Deuterophlebiomorpha ===\n*[[Deuterophlebiidae]] [[Frederick Wallace Edwards|Edwards]], 1922\n=== Infraorder Nymphomyiomorpha ===\n*[[Nymphomyiidae]] Tokunaga, 1932\n=== Infraorder Tipulomorpha ===\n*[[Tipulidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1802<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iczn.org/iczn/index.jsp?article=11&nfv= |title=art. 11.7.1.3. ICZN |access-date=2007-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928063322/http://www.iczn.org/iczn/index.jsp?nfv=&article=11 |archive-date=2007-09-28 |url-status=dead }}</ref> \n*[[Cylindrotomidae]] Schiner, 1863 \n*[[Trichoceridae]] [[Camillo R\u00f3ndani|Rondani]], 1841 Synonym: Petauristidae.\n*[[Pediciidae]] [[Karl Robert Osten-Sacken|Osten-Sacken]], 1859 \n*[[Limoniidae]] Rondani, 1856\n===  Infraorder Ptychopteromorpha ===  \n*[[Ptychopteridae]] [[Karl Robert Osten-Sacken|Osten-Sacken]], 1862 Synonyms: Liriopeidae, Liriopidae.\n=== Infraorder Psychodomorpha === \n*[[Blephariceridae]] [[Hermann Loew|Loew]], 1861 Synonym: Blepharoceridae.\n*[[Psychodidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834 Synonyms: Nemopalpidae, Phlebotomidae, Trichomyiidae.\n*[[Tanyderidae]] [[Karl Robert Osten-Sacken|Osten-Sacken]], 1880 Synonym: Macrochilidae.\n\n=== Infraorder Culicomorpha  ===\n*[[Dixidae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1868\n*[[Corethrellidae]] [[Frederick Wallace Edwards|Edwards]], 1932 \n*[[Chaoboridae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834 Synonyms: Corethridae, Chironomapteridae, Mesotendipedidae, Dixamimidae, Rhaetomyiidae.\n*[[Culicidae]] [[Johann Wilhelm Meigen|Meigen]], 1818\n*[[Thaumaleidae]] [[Mario Bezzi|Bezzi]], 1913 Synonym: Orphnephilidae.\n*[[Simuliidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]],1834 Synonyms: Melusinidae.\n*[[Ceratopogonidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834 Synonyms: Leptoconopidae, Helidae, Heleidae.\n*[[Chironomidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834 Synonym: Tendipedidae\n=== Infraorder Perissommatomorpha === \n*[[Perissommatidae]] Colless, 1962 \n=== Infraorder Bibionomorpha ===   \n*[[Anisopodidae]] [[Frederick Knab|Knab]], 1912 Synonyms: Phryneidae, Rhyphidae, Sylvicolidae, Mycetobiidae, Protolbiogastridae.\n*[[Canthyloscelididae]] [[G\u00fcnther Enderlein|Enderlein]], 1912 Synonyms: Hyperoscelididae, Synneuridae.\n*[[Scatopsidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834\n*[[Axymyiidae]] [[Raymond Corbett Shannon|Shannon]], 1921\n*[[Hesperinidae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1864 \n*[[Bibionidae]] [[John Fleming (naturalist)|Fleming]], 1821 Synonyms: Penthetriidae, Pleciidae.\n*[[Pachyneuridae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1864 Synonym: Cramptonomyiidae.\n*[[Ditomyiidae]] Kylin, 1919\n*[[Diadocidiidae]] [[Johannes Winnertz|Winnertz]],1863 \n*[[Mycetophilidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834 Synonyms: Fungivoridae, Allactoneuridae, Manotidae\n*[[Bolitophilidae]] [[Johannes Winnertz|Winnertz]], 1863 Synonym: Bolitophilinae.\n*[[Keroplatidae]] [[Camillo Rondani|Rondani]], 1856 Synonyms: Ceroplatidae, Zelmiridae, Platyuridae, Zelmicidae, Macroceratidae, Macroceridae, Necromyzidae\n*[[Lygistorrhinidae]] [[Frederick Wallace Edwards|Edwards]],1925 \n*[[Rangomaramidae]] Jaschhof & Didham, 2002 \n*[[Sciaridae]] [[Gustaf Johan Billberg|Billberg]], 1820 Synonym: Lycoriidae.\n*[[Cecidomyiidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1835 Synonyms: Porricondylidae, Itonididae, Heteropezidae, Lestremiidae, Campylomyzidae.\n\n==Nematocera families known only as fossils==\n*[[Ansorgiidae]] Krzemi\u00f1ski & Lukashevich, 1993.\n*[[Antefungivoridae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1938. Synonyms: Antiquamediidae, Pleciomimidae, Sinemediidae.\n*[[Architendipedidae]].\n*[[Archizelmiridae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1962.\n*[[Asiochaoboridae]] Hong & Wang, 1990. \n*[[Boholdoyidae]] Kovalev, 1985.\n*[[Cascopleciidae]]\n*[[Crosaphididae]] Kovalev, 1983.\n*[[Elliidae]] Krzeminska, Blagoderov & Krezmi\u00f1ski, 1993.\n*[[Eoditomyiidae]] Ansorge, 1996.\n*[[Eopleciidae]].\n*[[Eopolyneuridae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1962.\n*[[Eoptychopteridae]].\n*[[Gracilitipulidae]].\n*[[Grauvogeliidae]] Krzemi\u00f1ski, 1999.\n*[[Hennigmatidae]] Shcherbakov, 1995.\n*[[Heterorhyphidae]] Ansorge & Krzemi\u00f1ski, 1995.\n*[[Hyperpolyneuridae]]. Rohdendorf, 1962 \n*[[Limnorhyphidae]].\n*[[Luanpingitidae]] Zhang, 1986.\n*[[Mesophantasmatidae]].\n*[[Mesosciophilidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1946.\n*[[Musidoromimidae]].\n*[[Nadipteridae]] Lukashevich, 1995.\n*[[Oligophrynidae]].\n*[[Oreodomyiidae]].\n*[[Palaeophoridae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1951. Synonym: Sciadoceridae\n*[[Parapleciidae]].\n*[[Paraxymyiidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1946.\n*[[Pleciodictyidae]].\n*[[Pleciofungivoridae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1946. Synonym: Fungivoritinae\n*[[Procramptonomyiidae]] Kovalev, 1983.\n*[[Protendipedidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1951. Synonym: Prototendipedidae.\n*[[Protobibionidae]] F. M. Carpenter 1992.\n*[[Protopleciidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1946. Synonyms: Dyspolyneuridae, Protoligoneuridae. Palaeoplecidae\n*[[Protorhyphidae]] [[Anton Handlirsch|Handlirsch]], 1906.\n*[[Protoscatopsidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1946.\n*[[Serendipidae]] Evenhuis, 1994. Synonym: Paratendipedidae.\n*[[Siberhyphidae]] Kovalev, 1985.\n*[[Sinotendipedidae]].\n*[[Strashilidae]]. Synonym: Vosilidae.\n*[[Tanyderophrynidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1962. Synonym: Tanyderophryneidae.\n*[[Tethepomyiidae]] Grimaldi & Arillo, 2009 \n*[[Tillyardipteridae]] Lukashevich & Shcherbakov, 1999.\n*[[Tipulodictyidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1962.\n*[[Tipulopleciidae]] [[Boris Borisovitsch Rohdendorf|Rohdendorf]], 1962.\n*[[Valeseguyidae]] Amorim & Grimaldi, 2006.\n*[[Vladipteridae]] Shcherbakov, 1995.\n*[[Zhangobiidae]]. Synonyms: Palaeolimnobiidae.\n\n==Brachycera==\n===Orthorrhapha ===  \n*[[Nemestrinidae]] Griffith & Pidgeon, 1832\n*[[Acroceridae]] [[William Elford Leach|Leach]], 1815 Synonyms: Cyrtidae, Oncodidae, Ogcodidae.\n*[[Hilarimorphidae]] [[Samuel Wendell Williston|Williston]], 1896 \n*[[Vermileonidae]] Williston, 1886 Synonyms: Protobrachyceridae, Protobrachycerontidae.\n; Superfamily Asiloidea Latreille, 1802\n*[[Bombyliidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1802 Synonyms: Phthiriidae, Systropodidae, Usiidae.\n*[[Asilidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1802 Synonym: Leptogastridae.\n*[[Mydidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1809 Synonyms: Mydaidae, Mydasidae\n*[[Apioceridae]] [[Jacques-Marie-Frangile Bigot|Bigot]], 1857 \n*[[Evocoidae]] Yeates, Irwin & Wiegmann 2006 \n*[[Apsilocephalidae]] Nagatomi, Saigusa, Nagatomi & Lyneborg, 1991 \n*[[Scenopinidae]] [[Hermann Burmeister|Burmeister]], 1835 Synonym: Omphralidae.\n*[[Therevidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834 \n*[[Mythicomyiidae]] Synonyms: Cyrtosiidae, Mythicomyiinae.\n; Superfamily Rhagionoidea Latreille, 1802 \n*[[Austroleptidae]] Nagatomi, 1982 \n*[[Bolbomyiidae]] Stuckenberg, 2001\n*[[Rhagionidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1802 Synonyms: Leptidae, Erinnidae (sensu Evenhuis), Paleostratiomyiidae?\n; Superfamily Stratiomyoidea Latreille, 1802 \n*[[Pantophthalmidae]] Bigot, 1886 Synonym: Acanthomeridae.\n*[[Stratiomyidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1804\n*[[Xylomyidae]] [[George Henry Verrall|Verrall]], 1901 Synonyms: Xylomyiidae, Solvidae.\n\n;Superfamily Tabanoidea Latreille, 1802 \n*[[Athericidae]] [[Maksymilian Nowicki|Nowicki]], 1873 \n*[[Oreoleptidae]] Zloty, Sinclair & Pritchard, 2005 \n*[[Pelecorhynchidae]] [[G\u00fcnther Enderlein|Enderlein]], 1922 \n*[[Tabanidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1802\n; Superfamily Xylophagoidea Fall\u00e9n, 1810 \n*[[Xylophagidae]] [[Carl Fredrik Fall\u00e9n|Fall\u00e9n]], 1810 Synonyms: Heterostomidae, Exeretonevridae, Exerotonevridae, Erinniidae ?(sensu Schumann), Rachiceridae, Coenomyidae, Coenomyiidae.\n; Superfamily Empidoidea Latreille, 1804 \n*[[Atelestidae]] [[Willi Hennig|Hennig]], 1970 \n*[[Dolichopodidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1809 Synonym: Microphoridae \n*[[Empididae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1804 Synonym: Empidae.\n*[[Homalocnemiidae]] [[James Edward Collin|Collin]], 1928 \n*[[Hybotidae]] [[Justin Pierre Marie Macquart|Macquart]],1823 \n*[[Oreogetonidae]] Chv\u00e1la, 1976 \n*[[Ragadidae]] Sinclair, 2016\n; Superfamily Apystomyioidea Nagatomi & Liu, 1994 \n*[[Apystomyiidae]] Nagatomi & Liu, 1994 \n=== Aschiza ===\n;Superfamily Phoroidea Curtis, 1833 \n*[[Ironomyiidae]] McAlpine & Martin, 1966 \n*[[Lonchopteridae]] [[Justin Pierre Marie Macquart|Macquart]], 1823 Synonym: Musidoridae.\n*[[Opetiidae]] [[Camillo R\u00f3ndani|Rondani]], 1856\n*[[Phoridae]] [[John Curtis (entomologist)|Curtis]], 1833 Synonyms: Termitoxeniidae.\n*[[Platypezidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1829 Synonym: Clythiidae.\n;Superfamily Syrphoidea Latreille, 1802 \n*[[Pipunculidae]] [[Francis Walker (entomologist)|Walker]], 1834 Synonyms: Dorylaidae, Dorilaidae.\n*[[Syrphidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1802\n\n=== Schizophora ===\n*[[Conopidae]] [[Pierre Andr\u00e9 Latreille|Latreille]], 1802 Synonym: Stylogastridae.\n==== Acalyptratae ====\n; Superfamily Carnoidea Newman, 1834 \n*[[Australimyzidae]] Griffiths, 1972 \n*[[Braulidae]] [[Johann Egger|Egger]], 1853 \n*[[Canacidae]] Jones, 1906 Synonyms: Canaceidae, Tethinidae.\n*[[Carnidae]] [[Edward Newman (entomologist)|Newman]], 1834\n*[[Chloropidae]] [[Camillo R\u00f3ndani|Rondani]], 1856 Synonyms: Siphonellopsidae, Oscinidae.\n*[[Inbiomyiidae]] Buck, 2006 \n*[[Milichiidae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1862 Synonym: Phyllomyzidae.\n; Superfamily Ephydroidea Zetterstedt, 1837 \n*[[Camillidae]] [[Richard Karl Hjalmar Frey|Frey]], 1921\n*[[Curtonotidae]] [[G\u00fcnther Enderlein|Enderlein]], 1914 Synonym: Cyrtonotidae\n*[[Diastatidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1917 (including [[Campichoetidae]])\n*[[Drosophilidae]] [[Camillo R\u00f3ndani|Rondani]], 1856\n*[[Ephydridae]] [[Johan Wilhelm Zetterstedt|Zetterstedt]], 1837 Synonyms: Risidae, Risiidae.\n*[[Mormotomyiidae]] [[Ernest Edward Austen|Austen, 1936]]\n; Superfamily Lauxanioidea Macquart, 1835 \n*[[Celyphidae]] [[Jacques-Marie-Frangile Bigot|Bigot]], 1852\n*[[Chamaemyiidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1910 Synonyms: Ochthiphilidae, Ochthiphilidae.\n*[[Cremifaniidae]] McAlpine, 1963\n*[[Lauxaniidae]] [[Justin Pierre Marie Macquart|Macquart]], 1835 Synonym: Sapromyzidae.\n; Superfamily Lonchaeoidea\n*[[Cryptochetidae]]\n*[[Lonchaeidae]]\n; Superfamily Nerioidea Westwood, 1840 \n*[[Cypselosomatidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1931 Synonyms: Pseudopomyzidae [[Richard Karl Hjalmar Frey|Frey]], 1941\n*[[Micropezidae]] [[\u00c9mile Blanchard|Blanchard]], 1840 Synonyms: Calobatidae, Taeniapteridae, Tylidae, Trepidariidae.\n*[[Neriidae]] [[John Obadiah Westwood|Westwood]], 1840\n; Superfamily Opomyzoidea Fall\u00e9n, 1820 \n*[[Acartophthalmidae]] [[Leander Czerny|Czerny]], 1928 \n*[[Agromyzidae]] [[Carl Fredrik Fall\u00e9n|Fall\u00e9n]], 1823 Synonym: Phytomyzidae\n*[[Anthomyzidae]] [[Leander Czerny|Czerny]], 1903\n*[[Asteiidae]] [[Camillo R\u00f3ndani|Rondani]], 1856 Synonym: Astiidae.\n*[[Aulacigastridae]] [[Oswald Duda|Duda]], 1924 Synonyms: Aulacigastreridae.\n*[[Clusiidae]] [[Anton Handlirsch|Handlirsch]], 1884 Synonyms: Clusiodidae, Heteroneuridae.\n*[[Fergusoninidae]] [[Andr\u00e9 L\u00e9on Tonnoir|Tonnoir]], 1937 \n*[[Marginidae]] McAlpine, 1991 \n*[[Megamerinidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1913 Synonym: Megameridae.\n*[[Neminidae]] McAlpine, 1983 \n*[[Neurochaetidae]] McAlpine, 1978\n*[[Odiniidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1920\n*[[Opomyzidae]] Opomyzidae [[Carl Fredrik Fall\u00e9n|Fall\u00e9n]], 1820 Synonym: Geomyzidae (sensu Evenhuis, 1994)\n*[[Pallopteridae]] [[Hermann Loew|Loew]], 1862 Synonym: Eurygnathomyiidae.\n*[[Periscelididae]] [[Lorenz Oldenberg|Oldenberg]], 1914 Synonyms: Periscelidae, Stenomicridae.\n*[[Teratomyzidae]] [[Willi Hennig|Hennig]], 1969 \n*[[Xenasteiidae]] Hardy, 1980 \n;Superfamily Sciomyzoidea Fall\u00e9n, 1820 \n*[[Coelopidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1910 Synonyms: Phycodromiidae, Pycodromidae.\n*[[Dryomyzidae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1862\n*[[Helcomyzidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1924 \n*[[Huttoninidae]] Steyskal, 1965 \n*[[Helosciomyzidae]] Steyskal, 1965 \n*[[Heterocheilidae]] McAlpine, 1991 \n*[[Natalimyzidae]] Barraclough & McAlpine, 2006\n*[[Phaeomyiidae]] Verbeke, 1950 \n*[[Ropalomeridae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1868\n*[[Sciomyzidae]] [[Carl Fredrik Fall\u00e9n|Fall\u00e9n]], 1820 Synonyms: Tetanoceridae.\n*[[Sepsidae]] [[Francis Walker (entomologist)|Walker]], 1833 Synonym: Sepsididae.\n; Superfamily Sphaeroceroidea Macquart, 1835\n*[[Chyromyidae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1863 Synonyms: Chiromyiidae, Geomyzidae (part. sensu Schumann, 1965)\n*[[Heleomyzidae]] [[John Obadiah Westwood|Westwood]], 1840 Synonyms: Helomyzidae, Trixoscelididae, Trichoscelidae, Rhinotoridae, Chiropteraomyzidae.\n*[[Heteromyzidae]] [[Carl Fredrik Fall\u00e9n|Fall\u00e9n]], 1820 \n*[[Nannodastiidae]] Papp, 1980 \n*[[Sphaeroceridae]] [[Justin Pierre Marie Macquart|Macquart]], 1835 Synonyms: Borboridae, Cypselidae.\n; Superfamily Tanypezoidea Rondani, 1856 (7 families) \n*[[Diopsidae]] [[Gustaf Johan Billberg|Billberg]], 1820 Synonyms: Centrioncidae.\n*[[Gobryidae]] McAlpine, 1997 \n*[[Nothybidae]] [[Richard Karl Hjalmar Frey|Frey]], 1927\n*[[Psilidae]] [[Justin Pierre Marie Macquart|Macquart]], 1835 \n*[[Somatiidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1935\n*[[Strongylophthalmyiidae]] [[Friedrich Georg Hendel|Hendel]], 1917\n*[[Syringogastridae]] Prado, 1969\n*[[Tanypezidae]] [[Camillo Rondani|Rondani]], 1856 \n; Superfamily Tephritoidea Newman, 1834 \n*[[Ctenostylidae]] [[Jacques-Marie-Frangile Bigot|Bigot]], 1882\n*[[Lonchaeidae]] [[Camillo R\u00f3ndani|Rondani]], 1856\n*[[Piophilidae]] [[Justin Pierre Marie Macquart|Macquart]], 1835 Synonyms: Neottiophilidae, Thyreophoridae\n*[[Platystomatidae]] [[Ignaz Rudolph Schiner|Schiner]], 1862 Synonym: Platystomidae.\n*[[Pyrgotidae]] [[Hermann Loew|Loew]], 1868 \n*[[Richardiidae]] [[Hermann Loew|Loew]], 1868 \n*[[Tachiniscidae]] [[K\u00e1lm\u00e1n Kert\u00e9sz|Kert\u00e9sz]], 1903 \n*[[Tephritidae]]